ansilove
------------------------------------------
This is a complete rewrite of AnsiLove/PHP in the C programming language. It
converts ANSi and artscene related file formats into PNG images.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.0.7-1
  libansilove1-1.1.4-1bl1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.29-1
  cmake-3.14.5-1
  cygport-0.33.1-1
  gcc-core-7.4.0-1
  ninja-1.9.0-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/ansilove/ansilove

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/ansilove/ansilove/archive/4.0.3.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack ansilove-4.0.3-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./ansilove-4.0.3-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ansilove-4.0.3-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/ansilove-4.0.3-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(ansilove)
  /usr/bin/ansilove.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/ansilove.README
  /usr/share/doc/ansilove/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/ansilove/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/ansilove/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/ansilove/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/ansilove/THANKS
  /usr/share/doc/ansilove/TODO
  /usr/share/man/man1/ansilove.1.gz

